      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence index (GCI) study performed across three systematically refined meshes (4.2M, 11.7M, 31.4M cells). GCI for hemolysis index QoI is 3.8%, within the 5% threshold for MRL 2."
