      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented including blood analog fluid properties, rotational speed range (1800–3600 RPM), and flow rates (2–6 L/min). Traceability to ASTM F1841 confirmed."
